      h3.headline-4 Shared Responsibility is still your responsibility
      p When you deploy your workloads onto cloud service providers like AWS, Microsoft Azure, and Google Cloud, you are always responsible for a major portion of the compliance burden, predominantly at the operating system level. Addressing the gap is not rocket science, but is tedious and expensive. More importantly, it gives a reason for compliance officers to say "No" to using the cloud.
  .row.align-center.align-middle.group
