    .columns.small-12.medium-6.large-5.medium-order-1
      h3.headline-4 Interoperable data requirements interoperable infrastructure
      p Modern health IT is an ecosystem of solutions, which means digital health products must have a strategy to integrate with existing EHRs or other systems of record like PACs. Integrating with legacy on-premises systems is not easy when your architecture is on the cloud. Compliance, security, privacy, VPNs, and 1980s protocols are requirements for true interoperability.

